TICKING BOMB: Rank 3 Bomb

--Requires large Phys Rep that produces a loud ticking sound.
--Requires Marshal.

Place Ticking Bomb in an area. Declare a Tech Type.
Ticking Bomb will explode 5 minutes after being placed unless someone with the named Tech shuts off the bomb. (Takes 1 minute).
If Bomb goes off, all targets in the area are dropped to the critical stage of their Death Count.
All Upgrades on the area are destroyed.

[10 Telluric, 9 Fauna, 1 Gizmo]